{"tid":655134,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解日本出得咁少open world game?","createTime":"2018-05-06T08:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T13:04:12.000Z","uid":80323,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"80193a1c0a0fa01a21eb627a4e2fed7b6cc1ddfc","tid":655134,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:52:37.000Z","msg":"open world係國際主流既遊戲類型，除左gta,watch dog呢類open world之外，仲有open world rpg(例如fallout)、open world fps(far cry)同open world賽車(例如Forza Horizon)。<br />\n<br />\n淨係2015-2017呢3年，歐美已經出左15隻open world，分別係巫師3, Batman arkham knight, Assassin's creed syndicate, Fallout 4, Just case 3, need of speed(2015), Far cry primal, watch dog 2, Mafia III, Forza Horizon 3, American Truck Simulator, Horizon Zero Dawn, Ghost Recon Wildlands, Assassin's Creed Origins, Need for Speed Payback。(唔知有冇數漏)<br />\n<br />\n但係日本呢17年黎就淨係出得一兩隻open world，反而戀愛遊戲出得仲多，點解日本唔出國際主流既open world反而出咁多戀愛game?"},{"pid":"6cc19d25f9636bd4395d55833a7800a072dde060","tid":655134,"uid":5190,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T08:57:01.000Z","msg":"因為日本仔鍾意玩注重劇情嘅遊戲 而唔係自由度大嘅遊戲"},{"pid":"ba12501c409bd306dc731551c5a4c090129c3132","tid":655134,"uid":76854,"like":12,"dislike":8,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"又將一個國家同成個歐美比"},{"pid":"8cd0c92fc40eb4129cef02ab97555fc164293f2d","tid":655134,"uid":122997,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"啊仔,唔係玩沙盒一定好<br />\n好似evil within咁,第一集玩線性先至表現到果種恐怖感<br />\n第二集無啦啦加open world元素搞到成隻遊戲膠化晒(爭在冇加多人聯線可以成班人係條鎮度隊喪屍)"},{"pid":"b417ff3ab67cbb7b067e46770db91aacd22bff4f","tid":655134,"uid":12351,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"遲啲隻隻Open world又會問返轉頭點解隻隻都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c961910b68e633c0cc3ad16262cbf4573370eb3","tid":655134,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:39:54.000Z","msg":"冇資源 著重返遊戲性仲好過整個空殼啦"},{"pid":"a4e9c931cf0bee65d6760ba1b796b8d2d5316bf2","tid":655134,"uid":4060,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"望下真三八 我唔解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121002258b6f4b06dbd792159c5fdae7a42654a8","tid":655134,"uid":8659,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"大家起底啊"},{"pid":"1bd374b1e14879000cd500ef698ab97402eaa7d8","tid":655134,"uid":50935,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:18:05.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b4f4717decf20ef0b8e1185f3434f999fa8dfd","tid":655134,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"比較優勢<br />\n市場口⼁乛⼀⼀⼀⼁⼃⼂"},{"pid":"0030ce91a29805c689557ab4d83f7135090bd90e","tid":655134,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b4f4717decf20ef0b8e1185f3434f999fa8dfd","tid":655134,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"比較優勢<br />\n市場口⼁乛⼀⼀⼀⼁⼃⼂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:21:42.000Z","msg":"味"},{"pid":"374d6b03f526c6286406963f40cd1abba86ecbc9","tid":655134,"uid":80461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"點解一定要出open world game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b61d8aad7f35772399c05b25ea9f36d45b2cd02","tid":655134,"uid":86186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"上年zelda咪贏左GOTY囉"},{"pid":"bbd304de231a2c0a6dc5f659c04d94df6c71cc92","tid":655134,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"2b61d8aad7f35772399c05b25ea9f36d45b2cd02","tid":655134,"uid":86186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"上年zelda咪贏左GOTY囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"